{"serial": "41005", "department_serial": 40, "code": "BA2015", "class": "A", "name": {"en": "Organizational  Behavior", "ch": "組織行為"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Chen, Yung-Yee"], "ch": ["陳永儀"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 4, "session": ["5", "6", "7"]}, "loc": {"building": "I1", "room": "109"}}], "isRequired": true, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": 70, "department": {"ch": "企業管理學系", "en": "Department of Business Administration"}, "system": {"ch": "學士班", "en": "Undergraduate Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "英語", "en": "English"}, "card": {"ch": "全部使用", "en": "All"}, "assigned": 0, "selected": 48, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "組織行為在探討組織當中所存在的各種人類行為，包括以組織為中心的社會性特質與活動，以及組織內的集體性及個別性心理現象。課程目標為協助同學:具備對於組織行為相關的研究，理論，與應用有通盤的了解，了解個人、群體、與組織系統對人們在工作場所行為的影響，以及解釋，評估，與應用組織行為的原則與理論。", "en": "Organizational Behavior is concerned with the study of human behavior at work. It is the field of study that investigates the impact that individuals, groups and structure have on behavior within organization. It is the study and application of knowledge about how people act within organizations. It covers three determinants of behavior in organizations: individuals, groups, and structure. OB is an applied field. It applies the knowledge gained about individuals, and the effect of structure on behavior, in order to make organizations work more effectively. OB covers the core topics of motivation, leadership behavior and power, interpersonal communication, group structure and process, learning, attitude development and perception, change process, conflict, job design and work stress."}, "outline": {"ch": "(1) 09月12日課程簡介\n(2) 09月19日組織行為與多元化\n(3) 09月26日工作態度與滿意度\n(4) 10月03日性格與價值觀\n(5) 10月10日國慶日放假\n(6) 10月17日知覺與決策\n(7) 10月24日情緒\n(8) 10月31日動機\n(9) 11月07日期中考\n(10) 11月14日團體行為\n(11) 11月21日權力與領導力+團體報告\n(12) 11月28日溝通+團體報告\n(13) 12月05日組織架構與文化+團體報告\n(14) 12月12日組織改變與壓力管理+團體報告\n(15) 12月19日衝突與協商+團體報告\n(16) 12月26日 期末考\n(17) 01月02日獨立研究\n(18) 01月09日獨立研究", "en": "(1) 09/12Course introduction\n(2) 09/19Diversity and OB\n(3) 09/26Attitudes and Job Satisfaction\n(4) 10/03Personality and values\n(5) 10/10National Holiday\n(6) 10/17Decision making\n(7) 10/24Emotions\n(8) 10/31Motivation\n(9) 11/07Midterm Exam\n(10) 11/14Group behavior\n(11) 11/21Power and Leadership + Group presentation\n(12) 11/28Communications + Group presentation\n(13) 12/05Organizational structure and culture + Group presentation\n(14) 12/12Organizational change and stress management + Group presentation\n(15) 12/19Conflict and negotiation + Group presentation\n(16) 12/26Final Exam\n(17) 01/02Independent Study\n(18) 01/09Independent Study"}, "textbook": {"ch": "Organizational behavior, 18th global edition. Stephen P. Robbins and Timothy A. Judge. 華泰文化出版.", "en": "Organizational behavior, 18th global edition. Stephen P. Robbins and Timothy A. Judge. 華泰文化出版."}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "0", "en": "0"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授", "en": ["Lecture"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "期中考: 30％\n期末考: 30％\n團體報告: 30％\n參與: 10％", "en": "Midterm exam: 30％\nFinal exam: 30％\nGroup presentation: 30％\nParticipation: 10％"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "By appointment", "en": "By appointment"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "16+2", "en": "16+2"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "Independent study", "en": "Independent study"}, "domain": {"ch": "基礎知識\n\n\n、\n\n\n人力資源管理", "en": "基礎知識\n\n\n、\n\n\n人力資源管理"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "管理知識", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "獨立思考和解決問題能力", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "國際觀", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "永續發展", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "溝通能力", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "出席/課堂表現"]}], "en": [{"competencies": "Management Knowledge", "rating": "(5)VeryHigh", "assesments": ["Test/Exam", "Attendance/Performance"]}, {"competencies": "Critical Thinking 